==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Classicalism
<hw>Clas"sic*al*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
classical idiom, style, or expression; a classicism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Adherence to what are supposed or assumed to be the
classical canons of art.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Classicalist</ent>⟦br⟧
